casebody.data:
Guthorn, Respondent, v. Keller et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. February 26, 1891.) Appeal from fourth district court.

Argued before Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

A. S. Sarahson, for appellants. B. Hoffman, for respondent.

Mo opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to abide the event.
